      <title>欧洲天然气处于危机前水平有望刺激亚洲需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/european-gas-at-pre-crisis-levels-seen-spurring-asian-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格目前接近 2021 年 5 月能源紧缩开始酝酿之前的水平，业内人士警告称，这可能会引发亚洲需求强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/european-gas-at-pre-crisis-levels-seen-spurring-asian-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:05:29 GMT</pubDate>
